  <entry>
    <title>我最喜欢的 15 首歌曲</title>
    <link href="https://chuishen.xyz/01/MyFavSongs.html"/>
    <id>https://chuishen.xyz/01/MyFavSongs.html</id>
    <published>2024-07-13T04:01:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-07-13T14:44:27.764Z</updated>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h2 id=&quot;1-Like-a-Rolling-Stone-by-Bob-Dylan&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#1-Like-a-Rolling-Stone-by-Bob-Dylan&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;1. Like a Rolling Stone by Bob Dylan&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;1. Like a Rolling Stone by Bob Dylan&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;我最爱的英文歌曲，无需用语言过多矫饰我对它的推崇。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
